section.section:
The following are grounds for an immediate suspension of a hunting license or hunting privileges:
Knowingly making a false statement in a license application;
A second conviction for violations occurring on separate days within any 12-month period for violations of State or federal hunting law that are not administrative or minor in nature as determined by the Department;
Failure to submit a report or report to a checking station as required under this title or by regulation; or
Failure of a nonresident of the State to appear in court in accordance with a citation issued by a Natural Resources police officer, or to any other process issued by any court of Maryland, for a violation of this title.
